{"tid":126704,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"如果有個醫唔好既病 感覺做咩都係徒勞無功","createTime":"2017-02-19T14:19:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-20T13:05:15.000Z","uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0252b708a317afa175158b8d1f385766149b85fe","tid":126704,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T14:19:45.000Z","msg":"醫生話我有機會患上左隻腸胃病，要長期食藥控制<br />\n<br />\n雖然仲要等多幾個月先肯定到係咪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係我已經不斷係到諗<br />\n<br />\n如果真係有依隻病，咁做人有咩意思呢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我家底唔好，本身諗住做會計，考救護入境去賺取穩定生活<br />\n<br />\n有依一個病既話，紀律部隊應該考唔到，因為會check病歷<br />\n<br />\n又唔可以成日捱，要睇住個打壞廢體，驚會令病情惡化<br />\n<br />\n變相我既目標好難達成。<br />\n<br />\n咁跟住既後果就係我養唔起屋企，養唔起老婆。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我有個穩定發展緊既女友，我都諗緊好唔好同佢分手，廢事有機會累左佢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n感覺成個人好灰暗，要靠煙同酒麻醉自己先訓到"},{"pid":"91dd27c0ce6dd4c828d4252ec77723153b661ccc","tid":126704,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T14:24:33.000Z","msg":"吹水既我聽日仆街死"},{"pid":"c9a5f6f72b7be1a1e7687976146fbd14b15d73ca","tid":126704,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T14:24:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>吹水既我聽日仆街死</blockquote><br />\n除左飲酒食煙個part"},{"pid":"474067056ee9cfc6222186b03ef1586aafe0f23c","tid":126704,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T14:34:58.000Z","msg":"屌你老母出post都無撚人回<br />\n<br />\n屌那星"},{"pid":"81b9ab2f11e99b4daaf09f922a3d52f4707dbc7b","tid":126704,"uid":74497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T14:36:18.000Z","msg":"是福不是禍,是禍躲不過"},{"pid":"cb8f7a51a5ddc7c9d146ec7ecfac99600b306151","tid":126704,"uid":9253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T14:39:35.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"5a38f8d5a3264d09b5ee9812bd904087caac21e0","tid":126704,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T15:16:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加油</blockquote><br />\n多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6884a7cf39e419e8bbc3f48c08148699cc09617","tid":126704,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T15:55:22.000Z","msg":"last一推 推完就唔再理"},{"pid":"4ffc015ab314efc31e36c6bfa563356f56e5cece","tid":126704,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T15:56:28.000Z","msg":"咩病?<br />\n腸炎?"},{"pid":"eb1c4236244ba689134838fd7ac7700f12970ccc","tid":126704,"uid":32422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T15:59:06.000Z","msg":"同女友傾你個病 一齊拆掂佢<br />\n<br />\n仲有一定要考救護ga咩 我相信唔止得一條路呀巴打"},{"pid":"97abe63326361b642d41d916f3a7f9a3442bc72c","tid":126704,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T16:03:42.000Z","msg":"IBD? IBS? 好多藥出左 可以控制到"},{"pid":"c51a7c89dc06c5b042501c61ae60764765fbaa3b","tid":126704,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T16:05:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>IBD? IBS? 好多藥出左 可以控制到</blockquote><br />\nIBD呀<br />\n<br />\n如果真係中既話"},{"pid":"7f9f792c7ae77fcf798996871d8a91cc6d00236c","tid":126704,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T16:05:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同女友傾你個病 一齊拆掂佢<br />\n<br />\n仲有一定要考救護ga咩 我相信唔止得一條路呀巴打</blockquote><br />\n我就係唔想累到佢，佢值得更好。"},{"pid":"644c7925c0de300f3a4420e0a8092ffc7f05d0b8","tid":126704,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T16:08:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>IBD? IBS? 好多藥出左 可以控制到</blockquote><br />\nIBD呀<br />\n<br />\n如果真係中既話</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nIBD有得搞<br />\n不過生物製劑都真係要D錢&hellip;"},{"pid":"f79d670bda3cda11c177ed2d5ef7937b02531962","tid":126704,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T16:09:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cff670c86c59e0a6c4ef2d6fa7c6d6ce3118f8d","tid":126704,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T16:10:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>IBD? IBS? 好多藥出左 可以控制到</blockquote><br />\nIBD呀<br />\n<br />\n如果真係中既話</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nIBD有得搞<br />\n不過生物製劑都真係要D錢&hellip;</blockquote><br />\ncheck過啦 好似預十皮野到<br />\n<br />\n不過都係控制，無得根治？<br />\n<br />\n其實如果控制，有啲case好似淨係消炎個隻已經得"},{"pid":"a0f11322c5497e721e8421de80196f534f880e36","tid":126704,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T16:11:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>吹水既我聽日仆街死</blockquote><br />\n除左飲酒食煙個part</blockquote><br />\n真係唔好試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n放心，有咩事上嚟講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"267845762daa71673dc23a952315af0c33e57b29","tid":126704,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T16:12:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>IBD? IBS? 好多藥出左 可以控制到</blockquote><br />\nIBD呀<br />\n<br />\n如果真係中既話</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nIBD有得搞<br />\n不過生物製劑都真係要D錢&hellip;</blockquote><br />\ncheck過啦 好似預十皮野到<br />\n<br />\n不過都係控制，無得根治？<br />\n<br />\n其實如果控制，有啲case好似淨係消炎個隻已經得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個個人都唔同<br />\n嚴重既要做手術tim<br />\n大方向有錢既都係玩生物製劑<br />\n雖然係長期病<br />\n但係又唔洗諗到太灰<br />\n好多人都可以過正常生活<br />\n番工聚老婆都唔係問題<br />\n唔好太擔心啦"},{"pid":"b72cedf9b11ade7a480622e319da6214c3d05030","tid":126704,"uid":63944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T16:13:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ae98fc270327f19f2787565c65cf213b76fc899c","tid":126704,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T16:14:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>IBD? IBS? 好多藥出左 可以控制到</blockquote><br />\nIBD呀<br />\n<br />\n如果真係中既話</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nIBD有得搞<br />\n不過生物製劑都真係要D錢&hellip;</blockquote><br />\ncheck過啦 好似預十皮野到<br />\n<br />\n不過都係控制，無得根治？<br />\n<br />\n其實如果控制，有啲case好似淨係消炎個隻已經得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個個人都唔同<br />\n嚴重既要做手術tim<br />\n大方向有錢既都係玩生物製劑<br />\n雖然係長期病<br />\n但係又唔洗諗到太灰<br />\n好多人都可以過正常生活<br />\n番工聚老婆都唔係問題<br />\n唔好太擔心啦</blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都要過多3個月先確診<br />\n<br />\n到時再算 哈"},{"pid":"081a20ca2532230cf0d8df83ba751dcefcc47814","tid":126704,"uid":84960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T16:24:22.000Z","msg":"師兄，我冇你咁慘，但自知自己又蠢又樣衰，所以都唔敢諗結婚生仔D野啦，父母個代過左之後應該會去外國安樂死"},{"pid":"67710f9b460efe74b71ec9a84a57c99959e2a362","tid":126704,"uid":83757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T16:29:29.000Z","msg":"唔好因為咁而諗分手，如果佢真係愛你嘅話咁只會令佢更傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加油"},{"pid":"b4fffc0f4b30a60f1261bf0c75156ad0c770c9d6","tid":126704,"uid":85586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T16:33:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好因為咁而諗分手，如果佢真係愛你嘅話咁只會令佢更傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加油</blockquote><br />\nagger<br />\n如果佢好愛你的話<br />\n就算過程再差對佢黎講都唔會係個負擔"},{"pid":"88663d5a4e04b3eaa9fd366bfb140b8cd3813c4b","tid":126704,"uid":50088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T16:35:45.000Z","msg":"老老實實你唔報自己病歷佢撚知咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一年咁撚多人考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你唔係覺得佢會逐個逐個人check佢病歷呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你唔好周圍同人講你有病無人篤你無人知架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算真係比人篤到你話唔知個病要報咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為控制住左病情又冇大問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f142f7baa00be281843d538b246dd0140e04b8d","tid":126704,"uid":50088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T16:38:12.000Z","msg":"而且你長期食藥姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又唔係冇得救控制唔到病情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔洗咁灰喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}